commit.message:
Replace RandomState.permutation with RandomState.shuffle (#46)

resolves #35

This change addresses 2 problems with RandomState.permutation:
(1) it's slow due to unncessary allocation, copy and conversions
(2) it munges mixed-type iterables, turning iterables of Tuples
    to nested arrays and converting all values to a common type

The license used by the project requires all copies of the software to include a copy of the license.  A dedicated LICENSE file is a convenient way to do this that is easy to find by users.
